# Title: Invoke-Obfuscation COMPRESS OBFUSCATION
# Author: Timur Zinniatullin, oscd.community
# Date: 2020-10-18
# Level: medium
# Description: Detects Obfuscated Powershell via COMPRESS OBFUSCATION
# MITRE Tactic: Defense Evasion
# Tags: attack.defense-evasion, attack.t1027, attack.execution, attack.t1059.001
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/process_creation/proc_creation_win_hktl_invoke_obfuscation_via_compress.yml

CommandLine IN ("*system.io.compression.deflatestream*", "*system.io.streamreader*", "*readtoend(*") CommandLine="*new-object*" CommandLine="*text.encoding]::ascii*"